OL,3,CAlec Baldwin 'violated' gun safety on
OL,4,CRust film set, jury hears
OL,6,FThe trial of actor Alec Baldwin began
OL,7,Ftoday, as ITV News Entertainment
OL,8,Freporter Rishi Davda reports
OL,10,FAlec Baldwin "violated" rules of
OL,11,Ffirearm safety on the Rust film set in
OL,12,F2021, prosecutors told the jury in
OL,13,Fopening statements.
OL,15,FThe actor arrived at his trial for the
OL,16,Fshooting of cinematographer Halyna
OL,17,FHutchins in Santa Fe, New Mexico on
OL,18,FWednesday morning.
