OL,3,CAlec Baldwin 'violated' gun safety on
OL,4,CRust film set, jury hears
OL,6,FBaldwin has been charged with
OL,7,Finvoluntary manslaughter after he
OL,8,Fpointed a revolver at 42-year-old
OL,9,FHutchins when it fired and killed her.
OL,10,FHe could face up to 18 months in
OL,11,Fprison.
OL,13,FHe has pleaded not guilty and claimed
OL,14,Fthe gun fired accidentally after he
OL,15,Ffollowed instructions to point it at
OL,16,FHutchins, who was behind the camera.
OL,18,FUnaware it contained a live round,
OL,19,FBaldwin said he pulled back the
OL,20,Fhammer, not the trigger, and it
OL,21,Fdischarged.
