OL,3,CAlec Baldwin 'violated' gun safety on
OL,4,CRust film set, jury hears
OL,6,FIn her opening statements, prosecutor
OL,7,FErlinda Johnson accused Baldwin of
OL,8,Fplaying "make-believe with a real gun".
OL,10,F"The evidence will show that like in
OL,11,Fmany workplaces, there are people who
OL,12,Fact in a reckless manner and place
OL,13,Fother people in danger. That, you will
OL,14,Fhear, is the defendant," she added.
OL,16,FJohnson added that the company who
OL,17,Fdistributed the gun for film use said
OL,18,Fit went through quality control tests
OL,19,Fand that before arriving on set, he
OL,20,Frequested to be assigned "the biggest
OL,21,Fgun available".
