OL,6,F"He pointed the gun at another human
OL,7,Fbeing, cocked the hammer and pulled
OL,8,Fthat trigger, in reckless disregard
OL,9,Ffor Ms. Hutchins' safety," Johnson
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"The only true and just verdict in
OL,13,Fthis case, so that true justice can be
OL,14,Fserved, is a verdict of guilty to
OL,15,Finvoluntary manslaughter."
OL,17,FOn the hand, Baldwin's defence lawyer
OL,18,FAlex Spiro said in his opening
OL,19,Fstatement that the 66-year-old
OL,20,F"committed no crime".
