OL,6,F"This was an unspeakable tragedy, but
OL,7,FAlec Baldwin committed no crime. He
OL,8,Fwas an actor, acting. Playing the role
OL,9,Fof Harland Rust," Spiro said.
OL,11,F"An actor playing a character can act
OL,12,Fin ways that are lethal, that just
OL,13,Faren't lethal on a movie set.
OL,15,F"And I don't have to tell you much
OL,16,Fmore about this because you've all
OL,17,Fseen gunfights in movies and the
OL,18,Freason that can happen is because
OL,19,Fsafety is ensured before the actor."
