OL,6,FSpiro added that those responsible for
OL,7,Fensuring safety on set failed in their
OL,8,Fduties and said before Baldwin took
OL,9,Fthe gun for rehearsal, it was deemed a
OL,10,F"cold gun," meaning it had been
OL,11,Fchecked and was safe.
OL,13,FHe said: "Cold guns can't hurt people.
OL,14,FIt's impossible. Literally impossible
OL,15,Ffor a cold gun to hurt somebody.
OL,17,F"You don't need to worry even about
OL,18,Feye gear or ear plugs for that fake
OL,19,Fbang."
