OL,6,FThe defence also played script
OL,7,Fsupervisor Mamie Mitchell 911 call
OL,8,Fabout the shooting, she can be heard
OL,9,Fspeaking to someone in the background
OL,10,Fsaying"F****** AD. It was his
OL,11,Fresponsibility," with no mention of
OL,12,FBaldwin.
OL,14,FThe AD, meaning assistant director of
OL,15,Fthe film, Dave Halls, is expected to
OL,16,Ftestify on the witness stand during
OL,17,Fthe trial.
