OL,3,CAlec Baldwin 'violated' gun safety on
OL,4,CRust film set, jury hears
OL,6,FIn a criminal case related to the on-
OL,7,Fset shooting in March, Halls pleaded
OL,8,Fno contest to negligent use of a
OL,9,Fdeadly weapon, the terms of that deal
OL,10,Fincluded six months of probation and a
OL,11,Fsuspended sentence, prosecutors said.
OL,13,FHannah Gutierrez Reed, the armourer
OL,14,Ffor the film was found guilty of
OL,15,Finvoluntary manslaughter and sentenced
OL,16,Fto 18 months in prison.
OL,18,FThe film director Joel Souza, who was
OL,19,Falso shot and wounded by the bullet
OL,20,Ffrom Baldwin's gun, is among other
OL,21,Fcrew members who will also testify.
